n-left:0pt"><tr><td style="vertical-align:top; width:384pt"><ol type="1" style="margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt"><li style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt; margin:12pt 0pt 0pt 14pt; padding-left:4pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">This is an uncorrected transcript of evidence taken in public and webcast on </span><a href="http://www.parliamentlive.tv"><span style="color:#0000ff; font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt; text-decoration:underline">www.parliamentlive.tv</span></a><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">.</span></li></ol></td></tr><tr><td style="vertical-align:top; width:384pt"><ol start="2" type="1" style="margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt"><li style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt; margin:12pt 0pt 0pt 14pt; padding-left:4pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">Any public use of, or reference to, the contents should make clear that neither Members nor witnesses have had the opportunity to correct the record. If in doubt as to the propriety of using the transcript, please contact the Clerk of the Committee.</span></li></ol></td></tr><tr><td style="vertical-align:top; width:384pt"><ol start="3" type="1" style="margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt"><li style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt; margin:12pt 0pt 0pt 14pt; padding-left:4pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">Members and witnesses are asked to send corrections to the Clerk of the Committee within 7 days of receipt.</span></li></ol></td></tr></table><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 12pt; text-align:center"><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt; text-transform:uppercase">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 12pt; text-align:center"><a name="bkEnd"></a><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt; text-transform:uppercase">&#xa0;</span></p></div><br style="c